'''布萊德·傑克森'''（'''Brandon T. Jackson'''，{{bd|1984年|3月7日|catIdx=J}}）是一個美國喜劇演員，[[底特律|底特律]]出生，雙親都是神職人員<ref name=cblaa>{{Cite news|last=Williams|first=Kam|title=Brandon on Breakout Role in Tropic Thunder|publisher=AALBC.com|year=2008|url=http://aalbc.com/reviews/brandon_t_jackson.htm|access-date=2010-11-25|archive-date=2011-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707072444/http://aalbc.com/reviews/brandon_t_jackson.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://familytreemaker.genealogy.com/users/g/r/i/Howard-E-Griffin-Greensboro/WEBSITE-0001/UHP-1313.html|title=Howard-E-Griffin-Greensboro - User Trees - Genealogy.com|website=familytreemaker.genealogy.com|access-date=2022-03-29|archive-date=2014-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141206105552/http://familytreemaker.genealogy.com/users/g/r/i/Howard-E-Griffin-Greensboro/WEBSITE-0001/UHP-1313.html}}</ref>。中學畢業後，他移居[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]追夢，開始時在{{le|Laugh Factory}}表演[[棟篤笑|棟篤笑]]<ref>[http://www.blackfilm.com/20050916/features/brandontjackson.shtml Roll Bounce: An Interview with Brandon T. Jackson] {{Wayback|url=http://www.blackfilm.com/20050916/features/brandontjackson.shtml |date=20160303231848 }} blackfilm.com, September 2005 (accessed 25 September 2007)</ref>，至2006年於電影《{{le|Roll Bounce}}》有一角色，並為他在非裔頒獎禮{{le|Black Reel Awards}}中奪得突破性表現獎。

